{"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/openswiftui\/viewthatfits\/hidden()"]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/ViewThatFits\/hidden()"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Hides this view unconditionally."}],"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI","doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/ViewThatFits"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"nonisolated","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"hidden","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"() -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"some","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"View","preciseIdentifier":"s:15OpenSwiftUICore4ViewP","identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/View","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"\n","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Return Value","anchor":"return-value","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A hidden view.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Hidden views are invisible and can’t receive or respond to interactions.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"However, they do remain in the view hierarchy and affect layout. Use","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"this modifier if you want to include a view for layout purposes, but","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"don’t want it to display.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["HStack {","    Image(systemName: \"a.circle.fill\")","    Image(systemName: \"b.circle.fill\")","    Image(systemName: \"c.circle.fill\")","        .hidden()","    Image(systemName: \"d.circle.fill\")","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The third circle takes up space, because it’s still present, but","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"OpenSwiftUI doesn’t draw it onscreen.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If you want to conditionally include a view in the view hierarchy, use","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"an ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"if"},{"text":" statement instead:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["VStack {","    HStack {","        Image(systemName: \"a.circle.fill\")","        Image(systemName: \"b.circle.fill\")","        if !isHidden {","            Image(systemName: \"c.circle.fill\")","        }","        Image(systemName: \"d.circle.fill\")","    }","    Toggle(\"Hide\", isOn: $isHidden)","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Depending on the current value of the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isHidden"},{"type":"text","text":" state variable in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"example above, controlled by the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OpenSwiftUI\/documentation\/OpenSwiftUI\/Toggle"},{"type":"text","text":" instance, OpenSwiftUI draws"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the circle or completely omits it from the layout."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"remoteSource":{"fileName":"HiddenModifier.swift","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/OpenSwiftUIProject\/OpenSwiftUI\/blob\/main\/Sources\/OpenSwiftUI\/Modifier\/ViewModifier\/HiddenModifier.swift#L283"},"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Instance Method","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"hidden"},{"kind":"text","text":"() -> "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"some"